1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,960
Why can't you just start the thing you know you need to do?

2
00:00:02,960 --> 00:00:04,640
Here's the part nobody tells you.

3
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:06,080
You're not avoiding the work.

4
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:08,480
You're avoiding the feeling the work gives you.

5
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:11,760
The boredom, the anxiety, the fear it won't be good enough.

6
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:14,400
Procrastination isn't laziness or bad planning.

7
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,640
It's your brain doing something much sneakier.

8
00:00:16,640 --> 00:00:17,840
And it has a name.
